ha: The Prophet prays eight cycles in forenoon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Hani\u2019 reported: I came to the Messenger of Allah, peace blessings be upon him, in the year of the liberation, and I found him taking a bath. When the Prophet finished his bath, he performed eight cycles of prayer, and that was in the forenoon. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 357,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25408,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/11\/three-regular-practices\/","url_meta":{"origin":36412,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Worship: The Prophet advises three practices","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: My dear friend the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, advised me to do three deeds and I will never abandon them until I die: to fast three days of every month, to perform forenoon prayer, and to sleep after performing the Witr prayer. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36412","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp